    "title": "Code Cuisine (cc",
    "version": "0.0.7",
    "description": "CodeCuisine is a .NET-based command-line tool designed to streamline common developer workflows from the terminal via a concise cc command. It provides a structured, discoverable command set and integrates with external executables to orchestrate tasks end-to-end. The tool emphasizes pragmatic automation and quick scaffolding for project essentials (e.g., generating standard configuration files like .gitignore) while keeping commands cohesive and easy to script."
